---
title: Bacon, Apple and Cheddar Melts with Honey-Mustard Dipper
description: Here's a bacon melt that's sure to be a hit with the whole family! Sweet apples help to cut the richness from the bacon and cheese, while BBQ-spiced potatoes get a honey-mustard mayo as a dunking buddy!
